# Backend origin the platform panel calls (spac/001_poc.md §7).
# Inlined at BUILD time — set it before `npm run build` (locally in .env /
# .env.production, or in the Vercel project env). The client strips a trailing
# slash and a stray `/api` suffix, so any of these work:
#   http://localhost:3000        http://localhost:3000/api        https://your-backend
VITE_API_TARGET=http://localhost:3000/api
